{"tid":1380287,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"墨刑，就是在犯人的臉上或者額頭上刺字和圖案","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T07:00:09.000Z","uid":284416,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ff3daee4031d4925b5c3ae0d455fa56423fd74","tid":1380287,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"分享下古代趣事<br />\n<br />\n墨刑，就是在犯人的臉上或者額頭上刺字和圖案，然後染上墨，作為受刑人的標<br />\n誌。墨刑其實對於犯人來說，肉體上的折磨並不大，可以說是最輕的刑罰之一了，但是古代往往很對人寧願不要受墨刑，因為這是一種恥辱刑罰，會讓犯人失去尊嚴，是一種心理上的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwHtCF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwHtCF8.jpg&h=92c32737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有d犯下重罪既人 俾人用半永久紋身係塊面上印左個洗唔甩既黑字<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係絕對對人既侮辱 以後唔敢見人返工 我極之反對千祈唔好咁做"},{"pid":"929fb1139507c566f8fa1bc2fe086b4c9ee72e04","tid":1380287,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5f346b851974122e711de81c468da3503d453d92","tid":1380287,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc2adeeca2c2c2e89ed7bf2cf59f1ee315e4c939","tid":1380287,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:10:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c29207727087b830d3e238bc1e45af007e2c5271","tid":1380287,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:19:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b75050aea9386f0436d28541bfa1d8edb00f481b","tid":1380287,"uid":284416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}